| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4705 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ff9d698e-b73b-5d57-89c1-e69d88e08ea2"
